@startuml 07-raci-matrix
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

title <b>Responsibility Matrix (RACI)</b>\nMapping Modules to Teams with Role Indicators

skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor white
    BorderColor #BDBDBD
}

map "RACI Matrix" as raci {
    Module => Team A | Team B | Platform | Ops
    Auth Service =>  R,A  |  C  |  I  |  I
    Payment API =>  C  |  R,A  |  I  |  C
    Database =>  I  |  I  |  R,A  |  C
    Logging =>  I  |  I  |  R  |  A
    Deploy Pipeline =>  C  |  C  |  R,A  |  C
}

note bottom of raci
  <b>Legend:</b>
  R = <b>Responsible</b> (does the work)
  A = <b>Accountable</b> (ultimate authority)
  C = <b>Consulted</b> (provides input)
  I = <b>Informed</b> (kept updated)
  
  <i>Each module should have exactly one Accountable party</i>
end note

@enduml
